{
  "stem": "20089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether it was to protect us or whether they weren't interested, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my first knowledge of what was going on in the war was when I actually arrived in Munich in 1946.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was out to have a good time and to get married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I studied social work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think I was the second group-- I was in the second group of students who qualified.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the South African Jewish War Appeal were looking for graduates to send to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody said to me, wouldn't you like to go overseas?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I'd love to go overseas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went off to the Jewish War Appeal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they asked me my age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said I was 25, which I wasn't, and they didn't query it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must've been 23 or 22 at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 1946.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I was born in 1925, I was 23.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if I was born in 1924, I was 24.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't ask for birth certificates, and I didn't have one anyway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were so few social workers who had graduated that they grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and so I went via London to Paris, and from Paris to Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my-- I was under UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But actually, because it was the South African Jewish War Appeal that sent me, I was attached to AJDC, which was the American Joint Distribution Committee, which was working with the Jewish displaced persons in Germany and elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "UNRRA was the United Nations Relief Rehabilitation Administration, which was at the head of all the private organizations like AJDC, and then the Jewish Agency, which came from Palestine.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
